[60.070435, "o", "  OK  XtraGPT-7B (local, fine-tuned on paper revision)               1.93s 148t\r\n  OK  Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct (local, XtraGPT's base model, no revisio   2.01s 152t\r\n  OK  GLM-5.1 (z.ai, general-purpose ~hundreds-of-B class)          19.73s 210t\r\n\r\n=== Task 2 — Introduction paragraph: reduce overclaim, strengthen motivation ===\r\n(prompt chars: 13603)\r\n  OK  XtraGPT-7B (local, fine-tuned on paper revision)               2.38s 186t\r\n  OK  Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct (local, XtraGPT's base model, no revisio   3.52s 280t\r\n  OK  GLM-5.1 (z.ai, general-purpose ~hundreds-of-B class)          16.54s 259t\r\n\r\nwrote /shared/hdd/nuochen/upload/XtraGPT/tests/openclaw-demo/outputs/before_after.md\r\nwrote /shared/hdd/nuochen/upload/XtraGPT/tests/openclaw-demo/outputs/before_after.json\r\n"]
[62.073645, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m── 6. The side-by-side report ──\u001b[0m\r\n"]
